headline: NFL and Zebra Technologies Provide a Preview of Super Bowl LX Using Next Gen Stats
summary: LINCOLNSHIRE, Ill., January 30, 2026--Zebra Technologies Corporation (NASDAQ: ZBRA) a global leader in digitizing and automating frontline workflows, today announced it will host its annual Super Bowl press conference on Wednesday, Feb. 4 from 1-2pm pacific.
